org.sql: SELECT users.* FROM users WHERE LOWER(users.login) LIKE LOWER('%Leonardo da Vinci%') OR users.id IN (SELECT user_id FROM email_addresses WHERE LOWER(address) LIKE LOWER('%Leonardo da Vinci%')) OR (LOWER(users.firstname) LIKE LOWER('%Leonardo%') OR LOWER(users.lastname) LIKE LOWER('%Leonardo%')) AND (LOWER(users.firstname) LIKE LOWER('%da%') OR LOWER(users.lastname) LIKE LOWER('%da%')) AND (LOWER(users.firstname) LIKE LOWER('%Vinci%') OR LOWER(users.lastname) LIKE LOWER('%Vinci%')) ORDER BY users.id ASC LIMIT "$1"
